<h2>kitsch</h2>
<p>What is kitsch?</p>
<p>Is kitsch the opposite of art?</p>
<p>Is kitsch the opposite of abstraction?</p>
<p>Is kitsch the opposite of the flow?</p>
<p>Is kitsch the opposite of the universe?</p>
<p>Is kitsch the opposite of the divine?</p>
<p>Is kitsch the opposite of the infinite?</p>
<p>Is kitsch the opposite of the subjective?</p>
<p>Is kitsch the opposite of the objective?</p>
